description:
This market will resolve to the contestant or group who wins Uuden Musiikin Kilpailu (UMK) 2026.

If at any point it is impossible for the listed candidate to win UMK 2026 based on the rules of the competition (i.e. they are eliminated), this market may immediately resolve to "No".

If no winner is announced by March 31, 2026, 11:59 PM ET, this market will resolve "Other". All ties will be broken according to official UMK rules.

The primary resolution source for this market will be official information from Eurovision (https://www.eurovision.com/), including live footage of UMK 2026, however a consensus of credible reporting will suffice.
